<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Invitation to Join FFNO</title>
</head>
<body>
    <table style="max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">
        <tr>
            <td style="text-align: center;">
                <h2>Invitation to Join FFNO</h2>
            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td>
                <p>Hi {{tenantName}},</p>
                <p>{{landlordName}} has invited you to join his/her contact network on FFNO.</p>
                <p>By joining {{landlordName}}'s contact network, you'll be able to communicate easily regarding any property-related matters and stay updated on important announcements.</p>
                <p>If you would like to accept this invitation, please click the link below:</p>
                <p><a href="{{invitationLink}}">{{invitationLink}}</a></p>
                <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, feel free to reach out to {{landlordName}}.</p>
                <p>Best regards,<br>The FFNO Team</p>
            </td>
        </tr>
    </table>
</body>
</html>
